      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AGASSI (1) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (22.60) behind Merl's Lad at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Sure to be about the mark. SUNSET WORM (4) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (22.98) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can feature with the right run. GO BOY (7) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing one length behind Speedy Cruella in 22.93 and recording a new PB here. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. AKRON ROCKET (8) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
